{"tid":740273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【泰洞後續】泰國被困少足集中討論","createTime":"2018-07-12T17:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T16:52:04.000Z","uid":153946,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd42f4258e5106951e515edf126f1ca3414f60d","tid":740273,"uid":153946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"隨著少年同教練悉數被救出 呢個po主要係希望集中返後續嘅新聞同消息 例如佢地嘅康復狀況、泰國政府嘅反應同發表嘅野(如有)、唔同傳媒嘅消息 等等。<br />\n<br />\n因為留意到佢地被救晒之後 上一個po亦咁啱1001 同時亦冇一個集中討論嘅po 集合返泰洞少足嘅後續消息<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位"},{"pid":"5432fe01e1febc234820b68d18a517a1176ba3e1","tid":740273,"uid":100368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e41709808edb8803f34b737bee8042288a524e3","tid":740273,"uid":153946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似乎太夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (本身想聽朝開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"ccd89f4aab44ba7b6eae7069218ec0f424eb5901","tid":740273,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"5f8b6e592165117617219bcad8d676fc2463f7f9","tid":740273,"uid":25800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:16:50.000Z","msg":"終於有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c95214e8b127895aa7b7e48aa6968b9f25c306","tid":740273,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:19:38.000Z","msg":"依幾日不斷睇番有關video 訪問<br />\n見到洞入面真係幾危險<br />\n幾個工作人員抬一個細路出嚟<br />\n路又難行<br />\n體力差少少都攪唔掂"},{"pid":"4e45bc78633f0d2f9cbc0547364b17ba9a7e9ff1","tid":740273,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T20:24:47.000Z","msg":"有無video"},{"pid"